message:
Hi Bob,

I have a product available that I believe could really benefit you. I'm offering it at $12,000. This is a great opportunity considering its value. Let me know what you think!

Best,
Shiloh
Hi Shiloh, Thanks for the offer, but $12000 is a bit more than I'm willing to spend right now.  I'm interested in the product and would be happy to pay $9500.  Let me know what you think!
